Tweeps fear for their lives after a cat taxi driver from Bree has been trending. People went from laughing about this but now it has instilled fear into their heads, the more the testimonies shared, the easier it is for them to believe. Endless testimonials of creepy and outright terrifying cat taxi driver has made people question if there’re other creepy things happening in taxi rank. Some are suggesting the investigation be conducted by taxi marshals but some think that maybe they also know what’s going on and they’re turning a blind eye! But as we all know, truth can be stranger than fiction, or in cases like these, more horrifying and shocking than anything that could be dreamed up by even the cruelest horror scribe. If you are faint of heart, please consider that your warning. Thandoo created a thread, telling her side if the story and this is when people started testifying.        